  "brand": {
    "tone": ["trustworthy", "professional", "premium", "secure", "accessible"],
    "visualLanguage": ["light mode primary", "clean flat 2D", "dark hero sections", "pill-shaped buttons", "editorial imagery"],
    "industry": "Finance",
    "notes": "Payment network design. Uses a standard sans-serif font stack across all weights. The primary brand blue (#1434cb) is a deep cobalt used consistently for CTAs, links, and interactive states. Buttons are universally pill-shaped (border-radius: 1000px). Headings use lightweight (400) font weights for an editorial, premium feel. The design system includes a complete dark theme via [data-theme=dark]. Section spacing is generous especially on desktop (10rem vertical). Card designs range from sharp-cornered panels (0px radius) to softly rounded feature cards."
  }
